data.description:
Welcome home! This charming 3-bedroom residence has been thoughtfully upgraded to offer you the ultimate living experience. Nestled in the heart of town, you'll enjoy easy access to the vibrant downtown scene and stunning beaches. Enjoy the inviting kitchen that seamlessly opens up to the dining and living area creating the perfect blend for relaxing and unwinding. Retreat to your own backyard oasis with a large screened and covered area great for outdoor living and entertaining. 
This home offers a rare opportunity to embrace the excitement and convenience of urban living while enjoying the comfort and privacy of your own space. Seize the chance to make this vibrant abode your new home sweet home in the heart of town!
